          },
          {
            "nodeType": "paragraph",
            "data": {},
            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Encounter difficulty is based on relative total level of monsters vs participating characters. Difficulty should map to expected resource drain and tactical stress.",
